<br>
From now on, an individual MUST sign themselves up, and themselves ONLY. Guild leaders can copy the URL of the thread for sign up and distribute it to their members, but the individuals must sign up. This way, we get a better picture of who is able to come to the raid. <br>
<br>
We'll see on the next raid if this helps us with attendance or not. <br>
